description: Slicifer was the very first Slice of Pizza to lose their Cheese Soul when Pineaple Yurei began vanquishing Cheese from the Earth Realm. He became the very first "Angry Slice Of Pizza" and obeys only Pineaple Yurei's orders
Claude is a mischievous Mythological Tanuki. He befriends Piza Sukeruton and also is a Guide and Narrator through the Piza Sukeruton Multiverse
A Rollerskating Chimpanzee who was fired from a Saturday Morning Kid's TV Show but thinks the entire world is still watching Him
A test character of the Mutai category
Frankie Trouble is a head strong and determined young Woman who loves the Wu-Tang Clan and is Piza Sukeruton's best friend
